00:14:59.287 --> 00:15:00.870 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Money doesn't
make you happy.

00:15:00.870 --> 00:15:01.160 align:middle line:90%
>>BLOOM: Right.

00:15:01.160 --> 00:15:03.160 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: It's good to
have it to pay your bills,

00:15:03.160 --> 00:15:06.590 align:middle line:84%
but I've seen more
wealthy people miserable.

00:15:06.590 --> 00:15:07.250 align:middle line:90%
I really have.

00:15:07.250 --> 00:15:08.860 align:middle line:10%
>>BLOOM: Because you need
that sense of a commitment

00:15:08.860 --> 00:15:10.550 align:middle line:10%
to something far
larger than yourself

00:15:10.550 --> 00:15:12.174 align:middle line:10%
that is going to
expand all of humanity

00:15:12.174 --> 00:15:14.640 align:middle line:10%
and is going to do wonderful
things for your grandkids.

00:15:14.640 --> 00:15:16.690 align:middle line:84%
And in America, we
don't know that.

