We don't know that
the reason that ISIS,

00:15:18.750 --> 00:15:22.220 align:middle line:84%
the Islamic State
of Iraq and Syria,

00:15:22.220 --> 00:15:25.610 align:middle line:84%
is rolling up the
roads toward Baghdad

00:15:25.610 --> 00:15:28.360 align:middle line:84%
right now is because they
believe in a higher truth.

00:15:28.360 --> 00:15:30.424 align:middle line:84%
They believe that they
are part of something

00:15:30.424 --> 00:15:31.590 align:middle line:90%
much bigger than themselves.

