Hey, we are something much
bigger than ourselves, too.

00:15:34.530 --> 00:15:36.590 align:middle line:84%
Not only have we
added that extra 35

00:15:36.590 --> 00:15:39.407 align:middle line:84%
points to the average
IQ, we've made sure

00:15:39.407 --> 00:15:40.990 align:middle line:84%
that the poorest
paid worker in London

