is 9 times as high as it is in
an indigenous tribal culture.

00:15:53.695 --> 00:15:56.550 align:middle line:84%
We have accomplished
material miracles.

00:15:56.550 --> 00:16:00.450 align:middle line:84%
And we do represent the
next best hope of humanity.

