00:20:40.300 --> 00:20:41.360 align:middle line:90%
A peaceful war.

00:20:41.360 --> 00:20:42.770 align:middle line:90%
It is a war for creativity.

00:20:42.770 --> 00:20:44.680 align:middle line:90%
It is a war to advance mankind.

00:20:44.680 --> 00:20:47.232 align:middle line:84%
It is a war to pull even
